{"tid":1976226,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙高透露當年拒絕巴塞、拜仁、阿仙奴","createTime":"2020-04-17T05:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T09:10:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"794f584d115778117a27b1fd8aaf145842a8eb15","tid":1976226,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"現效力水晶宮的馬馬度沙高回想2013年離開出身地PSG，以1700萬英鎊身價轉投利物浦，過程中曾拒絕巴塞隆拿、拜仁慕尼黑、阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n為「紅軍」效力3個完整球季、上陣80次的沙高回想：「當我離開PSG，我有好一些機會，來自巴塞、拜仁、阿仙奴和利物浦。我選擇利物浦因為他們歷史悠久，而且是我夢想球會之一，我有機會在那裏度過4年，在了不起的球迷面前身披『紅軍』戰衣。而且，我跟管理層關係也很好，亦有幸跟蘇亞雷斯、古天奴、史杜歷治、謝拉特這些頂尖球員共事，十分快樂。」沙高2017年先是借用，後正式轉會水晶宮。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU94D442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=ebbd2941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"b955e608a9f6353a47c103c86c528bfebbdd7e84","tid":1976226,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38469bb3340a98db72df9e13890ee6d0c8538ae1","tid":1976226,"uid":103914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:59:38.000Z","msg":"加盟隊廢隊攪到自己咁<br />\n為左咩"},{"pid":"735fb6fd16363c1dcfcd7309b858278f08be9812","tid":1976226,"uid":161374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"想當年我都拒絕巴塞，本來成為本港第一個加入巴塞嘅人<br />\n<br />\n最後我選擇南華，因為他們歷史悠久，而且是我夢想球會之一"},{"pid":"144c5d18508dd1312874048ad8fde406f02049f4","tid":1976226,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b955e608a9f6353a47c103c86c528bfebbdd7e84","tid":1976226,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"笑西?"},{"pid":"2d710430212b6ce06e692bf9b837e3b39a564607","tid":1976226,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"